# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok former president george h.w. bush says the #### presidential race is so intense , it could bring on another brush with ulcers like those that afflicted him years ago .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "George"
                  :op2 "H."
                  :op3 "W."
                  :op4 "Bush")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)
                  :time (f / former)))
      :ARG1 (ii / intense-02
            :ARG1 (r / race-02
                  :ARG2 (p3 / president))
            :ARG0-of (c / cause-01
                  :ARG1 (p4 / possible-01
                        :ARG1 (b / bring-on-06
                              :ARG0 r
                              :ARG1 (b2 / brush
                                    :mod (a / another)
                                    :ARG1-of (r2 / resemble-01
                                          :ARG2 (u / ulcer
                                                :ARG0-of (a2 / afflict-01
                                                      :ARG1 p
                                                      :time (b3 / before
                                                            :op1 (n2 / now)
                                                            :quant (m / multiple
                                                                  :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                                                                        :quant 1
                                                                        :unit (y / year)))))))))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok testimony from the #### trial at which dr. sam sheppard was convicted of killing his wife was not tainted , and will be allowed at the upcoming trial aimed at clearing his name , a judge has ruled .
# ::alignments
(r / rule-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG3 (j / judge-01)))
      :ARG3 (a / and
            :op1 (t / taint-01
                  :polarity -
                  :ARG1 (t2 / testify-01
                        :ARG0 (t3 / try-02
                              :ARG1 (p2 / person
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "Dr."
                                          :op2 "Sam"
                                          :op3 "Sheppard")
                                    :ARG1-of (c / convict-01
                                          :ARG2 (k / kill-01
                                                :ARG0 p2
                                                :ARG1 (p3 / person
                                                      :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91
                                                            :ARG1 p2
                                                            :ARG2 (w / wife))))))
                              :mod (t4 / thing
                                    :name n
                                    :op1 "###")))))
      :op2 (a2 / allow-01
            :polarity -
            :ARG1 t2
            :location (t5 / try-02
                  :ARG1-of (a3 / aim-02
                        :ARG2 (c2 / clear-01
                              :ARG1 n
                              :poss p2)))
            :mod (u / upcoming)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok china 's benchmark shanghai composite index on the shanghai stock exchange closed at #,###.## points thursday , down #.## percent , or ##.## points , from the previous close .
# ::alignments
(m / multi-sentence
      :snt1 (c / close-01
            :ARG1 (ii / index
                  :mod (c2 / composite)
                  :mod (m2 / market-sector
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Shanghai"))
                  :poss (c3 / company
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Shanghai"
                              :op2 "Stock"
                              :op3 "Exchange"))
                  :mod (b / benchmark))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday)))
      :snt2 (o / or
            :op1 (p / point
                  :time (d2 / date-entity
                        :weekday t))
            :ARG1-of (d3 / down-03))
      :op2 (p2 / point
            :mod (p3 / percent))
      :op3 (p4 / point
            :time (c4 / close-01
                  :time (p5 / previous))))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok buddy kaye , a songwriter and lyricist who wrote hits for perry como , frank sinatra , dusty springfield and others , died on thursday in rancho mirage , calif. , where he lived .
# ::alignments
(d / die-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Buddy"
                  :op2 "Kaye")
            :ARG0-of (w / write-01
                  :ARG1 (s / song))
            :ARG0-of (w2 / write-01
                  :ARG1 (h / hit)
                  :ARG3 (a / and
                        :op1 (p2 / person
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Perry"
                                    :op2 "Como"))
                        :op2 (p3 / person
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Frank"
                                    :op2 "Sinatra"))
                        :op3 (p4 / person
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Springfield")
                              :mod (d2 / dusty))
                        :op4 (o / other))))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday))
      :location (r / ranch-01
            :ARG1 (m / mirage)
            :location (s2 / state
                  :name (n5 / name
                        :op1 "Calif."))
            :location-of (l / live-01
                  :ARG0 p)))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok outgoing un chief kofi annan is `` deeply concerned '' about the stalled peace process in divided ivory coast and calls on all political leaders to find common ground , his spokesman said wednesday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Kofi"
                              :op2 "Annan")
                        :ARG1-of (g / go-out-17)
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :polarity -
                              :ARG2 (c / chief)))))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (c2 / concern-01
                  :ARG0 (p3 / process-02
                        :ARG1 (p4 / peace)
                        :ARG1-of (s2 / stall-01)
                        :location (c3 / coast
                              :mod (ii / ivory)
                              :ARG1-of (d / divide-02)))
                  :ARG1 p2
                  :ARG1-of (d2 / deep-02))
            :op2 (c4 / call-03
                  :ARG0 p2
                  :ARG1 (f / find-01
                        :ARG0 (p5 / person
                              :ARG0-of (l / lead-02)
                              :mod (p6 / politics)
                              :mod (a2 / all))
                        :ARG1 (g2 / ground-02
                              :ARG1-of (s3 / share-01
                                    :ARG0 p5)))
                  :ARG2 p5))
      :time (w / wednesday))

# ::id 7 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok guided by american legal advisers , the iraqi government has canceled a controversial development contract with the russian company lukoil for a vast oil field in iraq 's southern desert , freeing it up for potential international investment in the future .

      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01
                  :ARG1 (c2 / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Iraq"))))
      :ARG1 (c3 / contract-02
            :ARG0 g
            :ARG1 (d / develop-02)
            :ARG2 (c4 / company
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Lukoil")
                  :mod (c5 / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Russia")))
            :ARG3 (f / field
                  :mod (v / vast)
                  :mod (o / oil)
                  :location (s / south
                        :part-of c2))
            :mod (c6 / controversy))
      :ARG1-of (g3 / guide-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (a / advise-01)
                  :ARG1-of (l / legal-02)
                  :mod c2)))

                                    :op1 "United"
                                    :op2 "States"))
                        :ARG1 c2
                        :mod (p2 / person
                              :ARG0-of (c4 / consume-01))))
            :manner (b / basis
                  :mod (w2 / worldwide))))
